      <title>电池初创公司 Sion Power 在 LG Energy Solution 领投的一轮融资中筹集了 7500 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/battery-startup-sion-power-raises-75-mln-funding-round-led-by-lg-energy-2024-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Sion Power 周三表示，这家电池技术初创公司在由韩国电池制造商 LG Energy Solution 领投的早期融资中筹集了 7500 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/battery-startup-sion-power-raises-75-mln-funding-round-led-by-lg-energy-2024-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 19:47:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称，2023 年加密货币黑客窃取了约 17 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/crypto-hackers-stole-around-17-bln-2023-report-2024-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Chainaanalysis 周三发布的报告显示，加密货币平台的黑客在 2023 年窃取了约 17 亿美元，比前一年减少了约 54.3%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/crypto-hackers-stole-around-17-bln-2023-report-2024-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 16:06:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
